title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Collect More New Vehicles
content:
GTA Online: Money Fronts features a collection of new vehicles to acquire, with a number of them debuting today in dealerships across Southern San Andreas.

Nimbly outmaneuver adversaries in the Annis Minimus (Sedan), get low with the Declasse Walton L35 Stock (Off-Road), or become the final boss of mid-life crises with the Declasse Tampa GT (Muscle).
